# ABEL TODO LIST

## Installation

- Clone the repository and move it into htdocs folder

```bash
 git clone https://github.com/ngar12/abel-todo-app.git
 mv abel-todo-app /c/xampp/htdoc

```

- Start your apache server
- Create a database with "todolist" as name. NB: make sure you dont have a password
- Import the todolist schema and data into your database
- View the project in http://127.0.0.1/abel-todo-app

## GOOD LUCK BRO !
